1.0.0.name: wordpress/nametag
1.0.0.description:
NameTag provides a business look-up for visitors' IP addresses and tracks those businesses through your blog, the pages they visit, and the search terms they have used to reach your blog.

This NameTag WordPress plugin allows NameTag customers to: * Automatically add the necessary JavaScript to their WordPress footer for tracking * With an API Key entered, allows users to view the latest 25 Companies who have visited their WordPress site.
